          <p class="mb-2">If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
          <div class="bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-semibold">RentGrab</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@rentgrab.com" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600">info@rentgrab.com</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="https://www.rentgrab.com" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600">www.rentgrab.com</a></p>
